                <p>We build systems that see and understand the visual world. Our work involves creating novel neural network architectures for tasks in image recognition, object detection, and medical imaging analysis.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="research-card">
                <h3>Time Series Analysis</h3>
                <p>Our research focuses on developing advanced methods for forecasting and recognizing patterns in temporal data. We tackle challenges in energy, and environmental sensor data analysis.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="research-card">
                <h3>Agriculture & Environment</h3>
                <p>We apply machine learning to address critical challenges in sustainable agriculture and environmental science, including precision farming, crop yield prediction, and monitoring climate change.</p>
